schema.name: drawCircle
schema.description:
Draw a circle.

Draw a circle with the given center and radius.

type.description: Type of the shape to draw.

x.description: X coordinate of the circle center.

y.description: Y coordinate of the circle center.

center.description: The center coordinates of the circle.

radius.description: The radius of the circle. Must be greater than or equal to 0.
